Class GoodService

com.example.paragonPioneerBackend.Service.GoodService
@Service public class GoodService extends SlugableService<Good,GoodRepository,GoodInput>
Service class for managing goods in the application. This class extends the generic BaseService to offer CRUD operations tailored to the Good entity. It utilizes GoodDTO for data transfer and interacts with the GoodRepository for persistence operations.

  • Method Details

    • mapToEntity

      public Good mapToEntity(GoodInput goodInput)
      This method is used to map a GoodInput object to a Good entity. It uses the builder pattern to create a new Good object and sets its properties based on the properties of the GoodInput object. The name, remarks, and isMapResource properties are directly copied from the GoodInput object. The slug property is generated by calling the createSlug method of the SlugUtil class with the name of the GoodInput object.
      Specified by:
      mapToEntity in class BaseService<Good,GoodRepository,GoodInput>
      Parameters:
      goodInput - The GoodInput object to be mapped to a Good entity.
      Returns:
      A new Good entity with properties set based on the GoodInput object.

    • patch

      public Good patch(Good entityToUpdate, GoodInput goodInput)
      This method is used to update the properties of a Good entity with the values from a GoodInput object. It uses the patchHelper method of the ServiceUtil class to update each property of the Good entity. The patchHelper method checks if the new value is null before updating the property. If the new value is null, the property is not updated. This allows for partial updates of the Good entity, as any property of the GoodInput object that is not set will not affect the corresponding property of the Good entity.
      Specified by:
      patch in class BaseService<Good,GoodRepository,GoodInput>
      Parameters:
      entityToUpdate - The Good entity to be updated.
      goodInput - The GoodInput object containing the new values for the properties of the Good entity.
      Returns:
      The updated Good entity.
